Package io.opencaesar.oml

Interface PropertyValueAssertion

All Superinterfaces:
Assertion, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
ScalarPropertyValueAssertion, StructuredPropertyValueAssertion
All Known Implementing Classes:
PropertyValueAssertionImpl, ScalarPropertyValueAssertionImpl, StructuredPropertyValueAssertionImpl
public interface PropertyValueAssertion extends Assertion
A representation of the model object 'Property Value Assertion'. PropertyValueAssertion is an assertion that specifies a value for a property on an instance.

The following features are supported:

  • Owning Instance
  • Owning Reference
See Also:
  • OmlPackage.getPropertyValueAssertion()
